::Striker/Rex::

Omega's telepathic message catches Striker by surprise, the Maximal 
not noticing me missile coming at him untill in nearly hit. Striker 
jumps backwards, the missile sending dirt and debree flying at him.

"I won't kill 'im, but I'll sure give 'im a good chase," Striker 
mutters, activating his jets and flying off atter Alpha.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Rex jumps to the side, the missile scraping agains his leg. He falls 
to the ground, rolling and getting into a crouch as the missile 
explodes against the ground.

Rex sees Striker fly off after Alpha. He turns to Hot Rod. "You 
allright?"
